```

output:
Set the tag on the action, then stop by tag:

```typescript
const rotate = cc.repeatForever(cc.rotateBy(1, 360));
rotate.setTag(99);
node.runAction(rotate);

// Stop after 3 seconds
this.scheduleOnce(() => {
    node.stopActionByTag(99);
}, 3.0);
```

You can also retrieve the action by tag: `const action = node.getActionByTag(99);`

